Step 3: Running Dart

Now, open the bin folder and type cmd in the address bar as shown below.

CMD


This will open the Command Prompt with the current directory path of the bin folder.
Now, type the following command:

C:\>dart


Now we are ready to use Dart through the bin folder.
However, setting up the Path in the environment variable will make this process easier â€” allowing us to run Dart from anywhere in the file system using the Command Prompt.
